high_descs: Move to the fridge behind you
Pick up the egg from the fridge
Move to the sink to the right of you
Clean the egg in the sink
Move to the table to the left of the fridge
Put the egg on the table
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled cleaned egg on the table in front of the fridge.

high_descs: Turn to your left and face the fridge on your left
Open the fridge and pick up the egg inside then close the fridge
Turn to your right then cross the room head to the sink
Put the egg on the left side of the sink
Pick up the egg and turn to your right move forward then to your right walk straight to the table
Put down the egg beside the sponge on the table
anns.task_desc: Put the cold egg on the table

high_descs: Turn left walk forward slightly then turn left and face to the refrigerator
Open the refrigerator door and pick up the brown egg on the shelf and close the door
Turn around walk straight then turn left and face the sink
Rinse the egg off in the sink
Turn around and walk straight to the white table
Place the brown egg on the white table
anns.task_desc: Rinsing off a chilled egg taking it to a table
